 ffonto:protectingSpecificBuilding  rdfs:comment "Indicates focused protection efforts directed toward a particular structure."@en .
 ffonto:nozzleActivelyFlowing  rdfs:comment "Indicates that a fire hose nozzle is actively discharging water or suppressant."@en .
 ffonto:peopleEvacuating  rdfs:comment "An observation that people are in the process of leaving an area due to an emergency."@en .
 ffonto:TFRdefinition  rdfs:comment "Definition of a Temporary Flight Restriction (airspace limitation for safety or security)."@en .
 ffonto:sirensAudibleInAudio  rdfs:comment "Indicates that siren sounds are detected within an audio recording."@en .
 ffonto:distanceInMeters  rdfs:comment "A measure of linear distance expressed in meters."@en .
 ffonto:smokeReachedStratosphere  rdfs:comment "Indicates that smoke from a fire has risen into the stratospheric layer of the atmosphere."@en .
 ffonto:hasDescription  rdfs:comment "Associates an entity with a descriptive textual summary or definition."@en .
 ffonto:carsParkedFacingRoad  rdfs:comment "Observation that vehicles are parked oriented toward the roadway."@en .
 ffonto:assemblyAreaVisible  rdfs:comment "Indicates presence of a designated gathering or assembly area for personnel or evacuees."@en .
 ffonto:smokeVisibilityDistance  rdfs:comment "Estimated distance at which smoke visibility is reduced or obscured."@en .
 ffonto:containmentPercent  rdfs:comment "The percentage of a fire perimeter that is secured or contained."@en .
 ffonto:observationTime  rdfs:comment "The timestamp indicating when an observation or measurement was made."@en .
 ffonto:warningVsOrder  rdfs:comment "A distinction between advisory warnings and mandatory evacuation orders."@en .
 ffonto:retreatingDueToActivity  rdfs:comment "Indicates that personnel or resources are withdrawing because of hazardous activity."@en .
 ffonto:dozerCuttingControlLine  rdfs:comment "Indicates use of bulldozers to cut a control line for fire suppression."@en .
 ffonto:rainSupportsSmokePersistence  rdfs:comment "Notes conditions where rainfall may nevertheless contribute to lingering smoke due to complex interactions."@en .
 ffonto:heatIndexC  rdfs:comment "Heat index value expressed in degrees Celsius reflecting perceived temperature."@en .
 ffonto:lowRelativeHumidity  rdfs:comment "A condition of relatively low atmospheric moisture, increasing flammability of fuels."@en .
 ffonto:gridX  rdfs:comment "The X coordinate index in a grid-based spatial indexing system."@en .
 ffonto:infoURL  rdfs:comment "A URL providing additional information or resources related to an entity."@en .
 ffonto:audioClipCount  rdfs:comment "A count of discrete audio clips associated with an event or dataset."@en .
 ffonto:bridgePassable  rdfs:comment "Indicates whether a bridge is safe and usable for passage."@en .
 ffonto:mediaKeptSafeDistance  rdfs:comment "Indicates whether media personnel are maintaining a recommended safety distance."@en .
 ffonto:droneRestrictionNearWildfire  rdfs:comment "Restrictions or advisories limiting drone operations near active wildfire for safety."@en .
 ffonto:bridgeScorched  rdfs:comment "Indicates visible scorching or heat damage to a bridge structure."@en .
 ffonto:privateCarsPresent  rdfs:comment "Observation that privately owned vehicles are present at a scene or location."@en .
 ffonto:hydrantAccessibleAndConnected  rdfs:comment "Indicates that a fire hydrant is reachable and connected to a water source and hose."@en .
 ffonto:recommendedAction  rdfs:comment "A suggested course of action intended to mitigate risk or achieve objectives."@en .
 ffonto:hasTimestamp  rdfs:comment "Associates an entity with a specific date-time stamp."@en .
 ffonto:firePerimeterExpanding  rdfs:comment "Indicates that the mapped boundary of fire is increasing in area or extent."@en .
 ffonto:animalsBeingLoaded  rdfs:comment "Observation that animals are being placed into transport for evacuation."@en .
