 ffonto:mcleodInUse  rdfs:comment "Indicates that a McLeod tool (hand tool for clearing) is currently being used."@en .
 ffonto:beaterFlapperInUse  rdfs:comment "Indicates that a beater or flapper tool is being employed to extinguish flames."@en .
 ffonto:wildlifeAfterFireGuidance  rdfs:comment "Recommendations for protecting and managing wildlife in post-fire environments."@en .
