 ffonto:barricadesPosted  rdfs:comment "Indicates that physical barricades have been installed to restrict access."@en .
 ffonto:ashPitDefinition  rdfs:comment "A definition describing pits of smoldering ash that pose burn risks."@en .
 ffonto:trappedInVehicleGuidance  rdfs:comment "Instructions for individuals trapped in vehicles during fire or smoke events."@en .
 ffonto:buildingVisible  rdfs:comment "Indicates that a building is observable in imagery or situational reports."@en .
