 ffonto:vehiclesTurningAround  rdfs:comment "Observation that vehicles are reversing course or turning to avoid hazards."@en .
 ffonto:peopleVisible  rdfs:comment "Indicates that people are observable in imagery or reports for situational awareness."@en .
