 ffonto:heatIndexF  rdfs:comment "Heat index value expressed in degrees Fahrenheit reflecting perceived temperature."@en .
 ffonto:hasMoistureContent  rdfs:comment "Associates an entity with a measured moisture content value."@en .
 ffonto:shovelsOrHoesScrapingToMineralSoil  rdfs:comment "Indicates use of hand tools to remove vegetation to mineral soil as a fire control measure."@en .
 ffonto:busesPresent  rdfs:comment "Observation that buses are present, potentially for evacuation or transport."@en .
 ffonto:animalsVisible  rdfs:comment "Indicates that animals are observable in imagery or reports."@en .
 ffonto:reflectiveSignageVisible  rdfs:comment "Observation that reflective road or safety signage is visible and legible."@en .
 ffonto:modalityConflict  rdfs:comment "Indicates conflicting information between different data modalities (e.g., audio vs. imagery)."@en .
 ffonto:chargedHoseLineDeployed  rdfs:comment "Indicates that a hose line is pressurized and ready for operational use."@en .
 ffonto:outrunWildfireGuidance  rdfs:comment "Guidance describing actions if a vehicle or person cannot escape an approaching fire."@en .
 ffonto:hasTemperature  rdfs:comment "Associates an entity with a measured temperature value."@en .
 ffonto:spotFiresDetected  rdfs:comment "Indicates detection of new fires ignited ahead of the main fire front."@en .
 ffonto:airtankerVisible  rdfs:comment "Observation that an airtanker aircraft is present in the area of operations."@en .
 ffonto:chainsawsOperatingForFelling  rdfs:comment "Indicates chainsaws are in use specifically for cutting or felling trees."@en .
