ffonto:usesWaterSourceOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking water source usage back to the operations or facilities that used them."@en .
ffonto:isLocationOf rdfs:comment "A relation indicating geographic placement or position of an entity."@en .
ffonto:isSmokeComponentOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking smoke components back to the smoke source or sample."@en .
ffonto:isLandCoverOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking land cover classifications back to the geographic units they describe."@en .
ffonto:isZoneOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking zone classifications back to the areas or jurisdictions they apply to."@en .
ffonto:enablesOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking capabilities back to the enabling resources or conditions."@en .
ffonto:isResourcePlacementOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking resource placements back to the incidents or plans assigning them."@en .
ffonto:contributesToFireIntensityOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking contributing factors to the fire intensity measurements or models they influence."@en .
ffonto:animalVisibleOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking animal visibility observations back to the reports or imagery in which they appear."@en .
ffonto:createsPyroWeatherOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking pyro-weather events back to the fires or conditions that created them."@en .
ffonto:isSmokeObservationOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking smoke observations back to the sensor or report that recorded them."@en .
ffonto:fragmentsHabitatOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking habitat fragmentation records back to the landscape processes causing them."@en .
ffonto:isFuelOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking fuel characterizations back to the fuelbeds or vegetation they describe."@en .
ffonto:detectedBySatelliteOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking detections back to the satellite instrument or mission that recorded them."@en .
ffonto:isAerialResourceOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking aerial resource assignments back to the incidents or commands deploying them."@en .
ffonto:containsLandscapeFeatureOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking landscape features back to the larger area or parcel that contains them."@en .
ffonto:requiresResourceOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking resource requirements back to the operations or incidents that require them."@en .
ffonto:useOf rdfs:comment "A general relation indicating use or utilization of an entity or resource."@en .
ffonto:isEmergencyContactOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking emergency contacts back to the organizations or households they serve."@en .
ffonto:appliesToUtilityOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking policy applicability back to the utility or infrastructure to which it applies."@en .
ffonto:locatedOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking location assertions back to the features or entities located."@en .
ffonto:isSmokeComponentOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking smoke component descriptions back to the smoke event or sample they belong to."@en .
ffonto:isSoilConditionOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking soil condition observations back to the parcels or study sites reported."@en .
ffonto:isDependsOnWaterSourceOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking dependencies on water sources back to the systems or activities that depend on them."@en .
ffonto:reducesSpreadOfOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking spread-reduction measures back to the targets or areas they protect."@en .
ffonto:isVehicleDamageOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking vehicle damage records back to the incidents or hazards causing them."@en .
ffonto:isRoleOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking role assignments back to the agents or positions holding them."@en .
ffonto:usesGISOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking GIS usage back to the projects or analyses employing it."@en .
ffonto:indicatesEcologicalStressOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking indicators of ecological stress back to the areas or populations affected."@en .
ffonto:isClusterOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking cluster membership back to the cluster entity or grouping."@en .
ffonto:protectedOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking protection status back to the assets or areas that are protected."@en .
ffonto:causesHabitatLossOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking habitat loss events back to the causing agent or disturbance."@en .
ffonto:threatensFarmlandOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking threats to farmland back to the hazards or events responsible."@en .
ffonto:causesHealthEffectOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking health effects back to exposures or events that caused them."@en .
ffonto:isEnvironmentOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking environment descriptors back to the entities that exist within them."@en .
ffonto:dataProvidedOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking provided datasets back to the providers or collection campaigns."@en .
ffonto:evaluatedOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking evaluations back to the subjects or systems evaluated."@en .
ffonto:isContactOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking contact records back to the persons or organizations they reference."@en .
ffonto:prioritizesOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking prioritization decisions back to the plans or authorities that set them."@en .
ffonto:protectsStructureOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking structure protection measures back to the structures they protect."@en .
ffonto:isEmergencyKitOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking emergency kit items back to the kits or households that include them."@en .
ffonto:isFireBehaviorOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking fire behavior characterizations back to the fire events or model runs they describe."@en .
ffonto:monitoredOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking monitoring records back to the objects or sites monitored."@en .
ffonto:involvesFirefighterOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking involvement events back to the firefighters or crews participating."@en .
ffonto:isEvacuationRouteOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking evacuation routes back to the plans or jurisdictions that designate them."@en .
ffonto:isAudioObservationOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking audio observations back to the events or sources they document."@en .
ffonto:isIgnitionCauseOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking ignition causes back to the incidents they initiated."@en .
ffonto:regrowthOfSpeciesOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking species regrowth records back to the areas or treatments where they occurred."@en .
ffonto:trainedWithOf rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking training-with associations back to the model or technique used."@en .
geo:SpatialObject
    rdfs:label "Spatial object"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "An entity that has a spatial representation or location in geographic space."@en .

ffonto:RiskAssessment
    rdfs:label "Risk assessment"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "The evaluation of potential hazards, impacts, and likelihood of wildfire-related events or environmental threats."@en .

ffonto:evaluatesRiskOf rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain ffonto:RiskAssessment ;
    rdfs:range ffonto:FireEvent .

ffonto:evaluatesRiskBy rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:range ffonto:RiskAssessment ;
    rdfs:domain ffonto:FireEvent .

ffonto:evaluatesRiskBy owl:inverseOf ffonto:evaluatesRiskOf .

ffonto:NaturalFeature
    rdfs:label "Natural feature"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "A naturally occurring geographic or environmental element such as forests, rivers, mountains, or vegetation."@en .

sosa:Sensor
    rdfs:label "Sensor"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "A device, agent, or software component that observes or measures environmental or physical properties."@en .

ffonto:SpatialFeature
    rdfs:label "Spatial feature"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "A geographic feature or object that can be located or represented in spatial coordinates."@en .

ffonto:hasSmokeComponent
    rdfs:label "is smoke component"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Indicates that a substance or particle is a component of smoke produced by fire."@en .

ffonto:influencedByGroundwater
    rdfs:label "influenced by groundwater"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Indicates that an environmental condition or feature is affected by groundwater presence or movement."@en .

ffonto:hasZone
    rdfs:label "is zone"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Indicates that an area or region is classified as a specific type of zone."@en .

ffonto:sceneLocatedIn
    rdfs:label "scene located in"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Specifies the geographic area or location where an observed scene or event occurs."@en .

ffonto:usedAsWaterSource
    rdfs:label "used as water source"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Indicates that a natural or artificial resource is utilized as a source of water."@en .

ffonto:providesWater
    rdfs:label "provides water"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Indicates that a resource or infrastructure supplies water for consumption, firefighting, or ecological use."@en .

ffonto:providesWaterOf
    rdfs:label "provides water of"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Inverse - Indicates that a resource or infrastructure supplies water for consumption, firefighting, or ecological use."@en .

ffonto:fireLocatedAt
    rdfs:label "fire located at"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Specifies the geographic location where a wildfire or fire event occurs."@en .

ffonto:particulateLevel
    rdfs:label "particulate level"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "The measured concentration of airborne particulate matter present in the atmosphere."@en .

ffonto:coversSmokeDamage
    rdfs:label "covers smoke damage"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Indicates that an insurance policy or coverage includes damage caused by smoke."@en .

ffonto:waterSafeToDrink
    rdfs:label "water safe to drink"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Indicates whether a water source is considered safe for human consumption."@en .

ffonto:isWeatherObservationOf
    rdfs:label "is weather observation of"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking a weather observation record back to the location, sensor, or event it documents."@en .

ffonto:causesRegrowthInverse
    rdfs:label "causes regrowth (inverse)"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking recorded regrowth or vegetation recovery back to the disturbance or management action that caused it."@en .

ffonto:mayRequireRestorationInverse
    rdfs:label "may require restoration (inverse)"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking a site or feature back to the post-event conditions or assessments that indicate restoration may be needed."@en .

ffonto:usesModelOf
    rdfs:label "uses model (inverse)"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Inverse relation linking an output, dataset, or decision back to the model or modelling process that was used."@en .

ffonto:usedBy rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain ffonto:DataRepository ;
    rdfs:range ffonto:FireRiskAssessment .

ffonto:usedOf rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:range ffonto:DataRepository ;
    rdfs:domain ffonto:FireRiskAssessment .

ffonto:usedOf owl:inverseOf ffonto:usedBy .

ffonto:WaterHose rdf:type owl:Class ;
    rdfs:subClassOf ffonto:FirefightingResource ;
